            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Aelius <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Posido<lb break="no" n="3"/>nianus v<lb break="no" n="4"/><expan><abbr>ix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> XVI <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>men</abbr><ex>ses</ex></expan> VIIII <lb n="6"/>dies VIIII <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>Antonia <lb n="9"/>Saturnina <lb n="10"/>avia memor <lb n="11"/>brevis pieta<lb break="no" n="12"/>tis <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan> <lb n="13"/>ὅν οἱ θεοὶ φιλοῦ<lb break="no" n="14"/>σιν οὗτος ἀποθνή<lb break="no" n="15"/>σκει νέος
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Unterhalb der Inschrift Relief mit Jagdszene. Die Stele wurde im 4. Jh. in der Außenmauer eines Grabes wiederverwendet. Unterhalb der lateinischen Inschrift dreizeiliger griechischer Text. ILJug: Z. 5: VIIIII.</p>
